-- use existing price_requests_last in LOOKER_SCRATCH.LR$YVNGR1667574201998_price_requests_last
-- use existing shipper_feedback_cvs in LOOKER_SCRATCH.LR$YVHMS1667520350387_shipper_feedback_cvs
SELECT * FROM (
SELECT *, DENSE_RANK() OVER (ORDER BY z___min_rank) as z___pivot_row_rank, RANK() OVER (PARTITION BY z__pivot_col_rank ORDER BY z___min_rank) as z__pivot_col_ordering, CASE WHEN z___min_rank = z___rank THEN 1 ELSE 0 END AS z__is_highest_ranked_cell FROM (
SELECT *, MIN(z___rank) OVER (PARTITION BY "shipper_feedback_cvs.load_number") as z___min_rank FROM (
SELECT *, RANK() OVER (ORDER BY "shipper_feedback_cvs.load_number" DESC, z__pivot_col_rank) AS z___rank FROM (
SELECT *, DENSE_RANK() OVER (ORDER BY CASE WHEN "pickup_region.name" IS NULL THEN 1 ELSE 0 END, "pickup_region.name", CASE WHEN "shipper_feedback_cvs.bid_date_week" IS NULL THEN 1 ELSE 0 END, "shipper_feedback_cvs.bid_date_week") AS z__pivot_col_rank FROM (
SELECT
    pickup_region.name  AS "pickup_region.name",
        (TO_CHAR(DATE_TRUNC('week', CONVERT_TIMEZONE('UTC', 'America/New_York', CAST(shipper_feedback_cvs."BID_DATE"  AS TIMESTAMP_NTZ))), 'YYYY-MM-DD')) AS "shipper_feedback_cvs.bid_date_week",
    shipper_feedback_cvs."LOAD_NUMBER"  AS "shipper_feedback_cvs.load_number",
    AVG(CAST(CAST((shipper_feedback_cvs."BIDDER_RATE") AS DOUBLE PRECISION) / CAST((shipper_feedback_cvs."DAT_RATE") AS DOUBLE PRECISION) AS DOUBLE PRECISION)) AS average_of_bidder_rate_dat_rate
FROM stark_prod.recreated_tables.custom_trunc_price_requests  AS price_requests
INNER JOIN LOOKER_SCRATCH.LR$YVNGR1667574201998_price_requests_last AS price_requests_last ON price_requests_last.price_request_id = price_requests.price_request_id and
      price_requests_last.shipper_application_id = price_requests.shipper_application_id
FULL OUTER JOIN LOOKER_SCRATCH.LR$YVHMS1667520350387_shipper_feedback_cvs AS shipper_feedback_cvs ON (shipper_feedback_cvs."LOAD_NUMBER") = (nullif(price_requests.external_id, ''))
LEFT JOIN stark_prod.recreated_tables.lk_regions  AS pickup_region ON price_requests.pickup_state_code=pickup_region.state_code
WHERE (NOT (price_requests.is_test_quote::boolean ) OR (price_requests.is_test_quote::boolean ) IS NULL) AND ((iff((nullif(price_requests.external_id, '')) is null, true, coalesce(price_requests_last.is_last_priced,false)) ) AND (((( shipper_feedback_cvs."BID_DATE"  )) IS NOT NULL))) AND (((( shipper_feedback_cvs."BID_DATE"  ) >= ((CONVERT_TIMEZONE('America/New_York', 'UTC', CAST(DATEADD('day', -14, DATE_TRUNC('week', DATE_TRUNC('day', CONVERT_TIMEZONE('UTC', 'America/New_York', CAST(CURRENT_TIMESTAMP() AS TIMESTAMP_NTZ))))) AS TIMESTAMP_NTZ)))) AND ( shipper_feedback_cvs."BID_DATE"  ) < ((CONVERT_TIMEZONE('America/New_York', 'UTC', CAST(DATEADD('day', 14, DATEADD('day', -14, DATE_TRUNC('week', DATE_TRUNC('day', CONVERT_TIMEZONE('UTC', 'America/New_York', CAST(CURRENT_TIMESTAMP() AS TIMESTAMP_NTZ)))))) AS TIMESTAMP_NTZ)))))) AND (shipper_feedback_cvs."TOTAL_WEIGHT_OF_LOAD" ) > 10000 AND ((CASE WHEN (shipper_feedback_cvs."TRANSFIX_BID") = (shipper_feedback_cvs."BIDDER_RATE") THEN 'Transfix Bid' ELSE CASE WHEN (shipper_feedback_cvs."BIDDER_RATE") = (shipper_feedback_cvs."WINNING_BID") THEN 'Winning Bid' ELSE 'Non Winning Bid' END
 END
) = 'Winning Bid' AND (price_requests.source not in ('shipment_creation', 'auto_accept_reject') )))
GROUP BY
    (DATE_TRUNC('week', CONVERT_TIMEZONE('UTC', 'America/New_York', CAST(shipper_feedback_cvs."BID_DATE"  AS TIMESTAMP_NTZ)))),
    1,
    3
HAVING AVG(CAST(CAST((shipper_feedback_cvs."BIDDER_RATE") AS DOUBLE PRECISION) / CAST((shipper_feedback_cvs."DAT_RATE") AS DOUBLE PRECISION) AS DOUBLE PRECISION)) IS NOT NULL) ww
) bb WHERE z__pivot_col_rank <= 16384
) aa
) xx
) zz
 WHERE (z__pivot_col_rank <= 50 OR z__is_highest_ranked_cell = 1) AND (z___pivot_row_rank <= 5000 OR z__pivot_col_ordering = 1) ORDER BY z___pivot_row_rank
